data.description: Discover your own private oasis with this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home featuring a screened porch, perfect for enjoying the outdoors without any unwanted pests. The spacious yard is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, complete with a shed for storage convenience, a swing set for playful moments, and a trampoline for active fun. Whether you're hosting gatherings or simply relaxing in your own space, this property offers the ideal blend of comfort and outdoor enjoyment.
